languages.text: "Могу ли я сказать что-то о жизни мон-кай? Нет, твои слуги были мне не интересны в той же мере, что и тебе. Они... как-то жили в твое отсутствие. Кто-то умер. Кто-то добился чего-то малозначимого. Ничто не изменилось".

"Do I have anything to say about the life of the mon-keigh? No, your servants are of as little interest to me as they are to you. They simply... carried on in your absence. Some died. Some achieved various insignificant things. Nothing has changed."

languages.text: “猴子的生活，我有什么可说的吗？没有。和你一样，我对你的仆人完全不感兴趣。他们只是……在你不在的这段期间继续生活。有些人死了，有些人取得了某些微不足道的成就，什么都没有变。”
languages.original_text: "Do I have anything to say about the life of the mon-keigh? No, your servants are of as little interest to me as they are to you. They simply... carried on in your absence. Some died. Some achieved various insignificant things. Nothing has changed."

languages.text: 「モン＝ケイの人生について言いたいことがあるかって？いや。あなたの召使には興味がない。それはあなたも同じはず。彼らはただ…あなたの不在中にも人生が続いただけ。死んだ者もいたが、些細なことを成し遂げた者もいる。以前と何も変わりやしない」
languages.original_text: "Do I have anything to say about the life of the mon-keigh? No, your servants are of as little interest to me as they are to you. They simply... carried on in your absence. Some died. Some achieved various insignificant things. Nothing has changed."

languages.text: «¿Preguntas si tengo algo que decir sobre la vida de los mon-keigh? No. Tus sirvientes me importan tan poco como a ti. Han... seguido en tu ausencia. Unos han muerto y otros han alcanzado diversos objetivos insignificantes. Nada ha cambiado».

languages.text: "Darf ich auch etwas zu dem Leben des Chem-Pan-Sey sagen? Nein, Eure Diener sind für mich von ebenso wenig Interesse wie für Euch. Sie haben in Eurer Abwesenheit schlicht ... weitergemacht. Einige sind gestorben. Einige haben verschiedene unbedeutende Dinge erreicht. Nichts hat sich verändert."

languages.text: « Vous voulez savoir si j'ai quelque chose à dire sur les mon-keigh ? La réponse est non. Comme vous, je ne m'intéresse guère à vos serviteurs. En votre absence, ils ont simplement... poursuivi leur existence normale. Certains sont morts, d'autres ont accompli des choses que je qualifierai d'insignifiantes. Rien n'a changé. »

languages.text: "Mon-keigh yaşamına dair söyleyecek bir sözüm var mı? Yok. Senin gibi, ben de hizmetkârlarınla ilgilenmiyorum. Sen yokken... Hayat devam etti diyeyim. Kimi öldü. Kimi çeşitli ama değersiz işler başardı. Değişen bir şey yok."
